\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"&quot;你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=a8f050e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>    。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"3a0f47105a0a84a45a45b4ac4edaffb62c7d4889","tid":2085103,"uid":311048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdbf51a30e67441362e0fcb0c2f5dc31f0c162c4","tid":2085103,"uid":125898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12af2446522df66b13c1b987901732447f2ad348","tid":2085103,"uid":311048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19d2f8b820f2dc436de7a9f7a3f5e3a5b872bdc6","tid":2085103,"uid":125898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:04:35.000Z","msg":"點解要得人鐘意？<br />\n點解要唔好惹人厭？<br />\n為咩？<br />\n點解需要咁屈就自己？<br />\n唔鐘意咪唔好做？<br />\n咁做對你自己有咩好處？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azzcLJk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FazzcLJk.png&h=fcaa83cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NhnqmgH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNhnqmgH.png&h=ee5d9f54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CDxt3u2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCDxt3u2.png&h=fa6aa80b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KkCWP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KkCWP6.png&h=a5e3e72f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjR6P97.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k